# Adjust Typer Bot Duration

The user wants to reduce the execution duration of the typing simulation from 7-9 hours to 5 hours. This will be achieved by increasing the target Words Per Minute (WPM).

## Proposed Changes

### PoseFlow-Merged-Archive

#### [MODIFY] [typer_bot.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/PoseFlow-Merged-Archive/typer_bot.py)

- Increase `min_wpm` from 3.8 to 6.2.
- Increase `max_wpm` from 4.5 to 7.5.
- Reduce the "re-reading code" delay from (2.0, 6.0) to (1.0, 3.0).

